headline: Analyst bullish on ConocoPhillips on synergy potential
summary: Investing.com -- Analysts are bullish on ConocoPhillips (NYSE:COP) as Morgan Stanley (NYSE:MS) resumes coverage with “overweight”, while Mizohu upgrades to “outperform” given its underperformance since announcing its Marathon acquisition.
